{"tid":1656312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣西有化工廠爆炸釀4死　目擊者稱見到煙霧及飄浮碎片","createTime":"2019-10-15T13:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T14:07:30.000Z","uid":210140,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eee1f525a181e83d8909930ace1e519f4b7d066b","tid":1656312,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"廣西一間化工廠發生爆炸，最少4人死亡，6人受傷，當中兩人重傷，4人輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n旁邊的公司有負責人說，爆炸時傳出巨響，公司圍牆嚴重受損，出現幾個洞，窗戶玻璃被震碎。住在兩公里外的王先生說，聽到很大的爆炸聲，窗戶劇烈晃動。另一名目擊者就說，事發時在附近考取駕駛執照，聽到爆炸聲後見到天上有大團紅色及白色煙霧，亦見到碎片狀的物體飄浮，他與其他考生在教車師傅安排下到室內躲避。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的「廣西蘭科新材料有限公司」，位於玉林市陸川縣北部的工業園集中區，在上午11時15分左右發生爆炸。玉林市人民醫院一名工作人員證實，有傷者被送往該院，在急症室接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，廣西蘭科成立於2010年，經營範圍是生物材料、合成樹脂、固化劑、廢砂再生專用水處理劑等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486313-20191015.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486313-20191015.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=3d648c96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486313-20191015.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=87de240a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486313-20191015.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"abcfa282bf26e87565779dcd70b3cb2a9a171c89","tid":1656312,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ea2d613b458fa575862a3e8808241db67e44ae7f","tid":1656312,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abcfa282bf26e87565779dcd70b3cb2a9a171c89","tid":1656312,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi